    dc:title "Gaidropsarus mauli a new species of three-bearded rockling (Gadiformes, Gadidae) from the Lucky Strike hydrothermal vent field (Mid-Atlantic Ridge) and the Biscay Slope (Northeastern Atlantic)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458648>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458650>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458652>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458654>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458656>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458646> ;
