<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458648>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Gaidropsarus mauli n.sp., MMF 26955, holotype, 360mm TL, from the Lucky Strike hydrothermal vent site." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1458648/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458650>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Gill rakers on the first branchial arch, left side of holotype (a) and detail of fifth raker of the outer row (b)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1458650/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458652>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Schematic illustration of the cephalic lateral system and the lateral line of the paratype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1458652/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458654>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Premaxillary (a), vomerine (b) and mandibular (c) dentition of holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1458654/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458656>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Lateral and posterior views of blunt (a, b) and sharp (c) lanceolate premaxillary teeth of holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1458656/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458646>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Gaidropsarus mauli n. sp. photographed at the Lucky Strike hydrothermal vent site (upper) and holotype on board immediately after collection." ;
